<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
      /* Reset styles */
      body, html {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }
      
      /* Container */
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      
      /* Heading */
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #333333;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      
      /* Content */
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
      }
      
      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        color: #777777;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin: 10px 0 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Website!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%=name%>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for logging in to our website. We are thrilled to have you as a member of our community!</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, need assistance, or want to explore our website further, feel free to reach out to us. Our support team is always here to help.</p>
        <p>Once again, welcome aboard!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
